# Retailer Template Project

This is a React + TypeScript e-commerce retailer template project.

## Tech Stack
- React 18 with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- React Router for navigation
- Uses a 12-column grid system (retailer-12col-grid)

## Project Structure
- `src/pages/` - Page components (ProductDetailPage, IndexPage, TemplatePage)
- `src/components/` - Reusable components (RetailerLayout, Footer, etc.)
- `src/utils/` - Utility functions (gridUtils)

## Key Features
- Product Detail Page (PDP) with:
  - Product images with zoom
  - Color selection
  - Quantity input
  - Add to cart functionality
  - Shipping & policies information
  - Product description and details

## Design System
- Uses a 12-column grid layout system
- Max width: 1920px
- Padding: 48px on sides
- Colors: #333333 (primary text), #757575 (secondary text), #dfe0e1 (borders)

## Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode
- Functional components with hooks
- Tailwind utility classes for styling
- Semantic HTML with accessibility in mind

